;">What deep learning solved, and Transformers expanded on, is allowing mod=
els to continue to <strong>scale performance with more data</strong>. The q=
uestion then becomes: <strong>how do you get more good data?</strong></p><h=
3 style=3D"-moz-osx-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-font-smoothing: an=
